data.description: Discover this secluded retreat located in The Carson Highlands. This home is a treasure trove of amenities! With 2483 square feet of living space, 3 bd, 3 bth providing ample room for comfortable living. This home has been thoughtfully updated with modern finishes and amenities. Enjoy the serenity and breathtaking valley views of this quiet location in Mound House while still being conveniently close to Carson City, 30 minutes to Lake Tahoe and Reno.  Schedule a showing today to see the extent. The primary bedroom is on the first floor with a large ensuite.  There is one bedroom upstairs which includes an ensuite with two private balconies. The home offers a flex space downstairs that can serve as a home office, sunroom or can be easily converted into an additional bedroom. Feel at ease with a modern alarm system.  A 2- car attached garage, plus, two additional 1-car detached garages are a haven for car enthusiasts, providing space for vehicles and projects. In addition to the two detached garages, there are two outbuildings, an oversized carport, and chicken coop, perfect for a little farm. The possibilities are endless.
